<div id="article" class="article-new">
	<h1>The six skills every cook really needs</h1>
	</em>
</p>
<p class="tagline">Even for confident chefs, the most basic kitchen tasks can be the trickiest to get right. Holly Williams finds out how to achieve perfect results every time</p>
	<p class="author">
            </p>

		<div class="clear-o">
			<p class="info"><em>Wednesday, 5 May 2010</em></p>

			<ul class="article-tools">
	<li class="share"><a href="#">Share</a>
