			<li><a rel="nofollow" href="http://uk.buzz.yahoo.com/buzz?publisherurn=theindepende_417&targetUrl=http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/food-and-drink/features/the-six-skills-every-cook-really-needs-1962376.html&amp;title=The six skills every cook really needs - Features - Independent.co.uk" target="_blank"><img alt="z" src="http://www.independent.co.uk/independent.co.uk/images/bm-yahoobuzz-icon.gif"/>YahooBuzz</a></li>
